dr. caligari is an 1989 avant-garde erotic film by stephen sayadian starring madeleine reynal , laura albert , gene zerna , david parry , fox harris and jennifer balgobin .   it is a semi-sequel to the 1920 film the cabinet of dr. caligari .   the film details a disturbed doctor ( the granddaughter of the original dr. caligari ) and her illegal experiments on her patients .   originally , and briefly , billed as dr. caligari 3000 when it debuted at select theaters in 1989 , the film promptly faded into obscurity .   since it was released on vhs and limited betamax format , the title has been dr. caligari .   the film is considered a cult classic and has been shown as a " midnight movie " at various times .